        {
            "title": "低空經濟屬新質生產力戰略一環 葛珮帆：充滿活力新藍海",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"低空經濟屬新質生產力戰略一環 葛珮帆：充滿活力新藍海\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/974e06c1dc78434bfaa9604f6704e0af/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250110/_2025011014225146214.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">低空經濟屬新質生產力戰略一環 葛珮帆：充滿活力新藍海</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>是次低空峰會於港大舉行，期間港大與內地飛行空域管理公司上和科技簽署合作備忘錄，擬於飛行空域管理、人工智能、氣象等方面合作；此外大灣區低空經濟聯盟亦與深圳市航空業協會簽署戰略合作協議，在低空經濟產業開展合作。\n\n</p>\n<p>大灣區低空經濟聯盟會長、立法會議員葛珮帆指，低空經濟是國家新質生產力戰略的一部分，是充滿活力的新藍海，發展迅速，且能推動產業升級，希望峰會能協助與會者精準把握低空經濟發展脈絡，積極應對科技、商業及規範層面所帶來的新挑戰，同時找到前所未有的機遇。\n\n</p><h2>科研發展空間非常大</h2>\n<p>葛珮帆表示，低空經濟在科研上仍有非常大發展空間，而大灣區低空經濟聯盟正是在國家大力推動低空經濟和通行產業發展的背景下創立。她指聯盟的目標是聯合大灣區各地政府的部門、企業單位、學術機構等多方力量一起推動低空經濟的創新和發展，並通過資源整合，在資訊共享、技術研發、標準制定等多方面合作，以致力構建一個可以互聯互通、高效協作的低空經濟生態系統，目的是實現大灣區內的低空交通、物流等產業的全方位發展，兼推動大灣區成為全球低空經濟的先行者和示範區。\n\n</p>\n<p>該聯盟於去年9月成立，葛珮帆稱，組織成立以來一直積極舉辦多項與低空經濟相關的活動，包括一系列座談會、交流會，冀推動業界參與低空經濟監管、沙盒試點項目。此外該聯盟也已向政府提交了名為《以新質生產力構建灣區自衛城市群》的政策倡議書，亦曾約見由財政司副司長黃偉倫任組長的發展低空經濟工作組、向當局提出十項重點建議等，冀全方位推動低空經濟在本港落地應用。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關文章\n\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-finance/3418404/\" target=\"_blank\">港大與上和科技 成立低空經濟聯合實驗室 推動大灣區融合 蔡加讚：香港低空經濟發展里程碑</a>\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-finance/3418409/\">港大首辦低空經濟峰會 港大申作軍：冀引領低空經濟發展方向</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2046320/即時-財經-低空經濟屬新質生產力戰略一環-葛珮帆-充滿活力新藍海",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-10 14:25:47",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "低空經濟需解決安全問題 未來10年料10萬飛行器同時運作",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"低空經濟需解決安全問題 未來10年料10萬飛行器同時運作 \" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1c016c4a94d0f057cbecff1ce7a151ca/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250110/_2025011014230249618.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">低空經濟需解決安全問題 未來10年料10萬飛行器同時運作 </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>深圳市人工智慧與機器人研究院執行院長李世鵬表示，按照把地面交通的十分之一搬到低空推測，以深圳的城市體量計算，未來10年之內估計達10萬飛行器架次同時在低空飛行，這是一個巨大的規模，如何去管理亦是一個很大挑戰。\n\n</p>\n<p>他稱，如果可以支持10萬架次飛行器同時運作，兩兩不相撞，或兩個點突發情況沒有沖突的話，需要巨大的計算量，如何簡化該數據需要算法及人工智能的很多方法。他表示，安全問題未來必須要解決，是低空經濟發展的前提，當下低空經濟在全國火熱，而中央認為要適當降溫，就是要把安全問題提到議事日程。\n\n</p>\n<p>對於監管問題，他稱規則基於科學數據制定，和民航局交流時，該局稱深圳可以先探索出一條路，經過總結驗證可行再向全國推廣。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2046321/即時-財經-低空經濟需解決安全問題-未來10年料10萬飛行器同時運作",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-10 14:25:48",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "朱千雪未有計劃追B：搞掂呢個先 大讚老公落手落腳湊仔 提議新婚蔣家旻先享受二人世界再生育",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/bcb7b624ebe1885a0a2627a9e640ddcd/2025-01/tracyyy.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/c02ecd90cf1a71efa5205114c1ca0102/3d5133bbe0b746198d6c4b98cde0b7a1-522ab8b2f207d63d1a9458d9e5bdbea1-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-6780bc4ba8061\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-6780bc4ba8063\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"朱千雪未有計劃追B：搞掂呢個先 大讚老公落手落腳湊仔 提議新婚蔣家旻先享受二人世界再生育\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6934cab881f437f001787da5c3063305/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250110/_2025011014152142244.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">朱千雪未有計劃追B：搞掂呢個先 大讚老公落手落腳湊仔 提議新婚蔣家旻先享受二人世界再生育</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>朱千雪（Tracy）今日（10日）出席奧比斯•曼秀雷敦「蒙查查～食茶點」活動，與擔任司儀的林秀怡和過百位小朋友一起體驗蒙眼食茶點又玩護眼挑戰。曾千度近視的朱千雪，表示現在不會經常玩電話，亦會定期檢查眼睛，更盡量不會讓囝囝接觸電話。她說：「我讀小學三年班已經有三百幾度近視，以前成日睇書會匿喺張床蓋住張被度睇，可能養成壞習慣睇，近視唔敢同父母講，等到睇唔到嘢先檢查，之後近視加深，直至廿幾歲先做激光矯視，就會注重護眼。」\n\n</p>\n<p>Tracy坦言湊B好攰\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪出席「蒙查查～食茶點」活動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ba388fd050d35cc8fbe7a69202e3ad9a/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪出席「蒙查查～食茶點」活動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪分享小學時曾有300度近視。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b65de640398ffcad8e163b21507cecfe/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪分享小學時曾有300度近視。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪指現在盡量不會讓囝囝接觸電話。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/335c97471e0e2debfcb993a02d8d1bd9/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪指現在盡量不會讓囝囝接觸電話。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪表示以前成日睇書，更會匿喺張床蓋住張被睇。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7b6ae77a02a3381a94ace63c03a79a4b/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪表示以前成日睇書，更會匿喺張床蓋住張被睇。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪希望囝囝避免接觸電子產品。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7937e2ee6bff4fb96943c4327d3f5200/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪希望囝囝避免接觸電子產品。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪與小朋友們體驗護眼挑戰。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b1565564e4582405b4e261420fda8efa/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪與小朋友們體驗護眼挑戰。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"靚媽朱千雪\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/314169ad90a7ca71b462e22c056892cc/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_11.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        靚媽朱千雪\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪大讚囝囝好易照顧。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/069130eccf20302f978f6f8cadd90de4/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_12.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪大讚囝囝好易照顧。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"談到可會追生B，朱千雪笑說搞掂呢個先！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ef294bebf0ae29c49811160d12d6264c/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        談到可會追生B，朱千雪笑說搞掂呢個先！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪表示湊一個BB已經好攰。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/50379a73f653f41262f68720d64fef35/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_14.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪表示湊一個BB已經好攰。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"希望熟習些再生多個。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ce6874dcece17cc61aa22623a3ce1626/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        希望熟習些再生多個。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\" 對於可會鼓勵好友新婚的蔣家旻生B，朱千雪提議她們享受人生先。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1458cc96b0e80694a5d7c11b2cd9a109/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_16.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n         對於可會鼓勵好友新婚的蔣家旻生B，朱千雪提議她們享受人生先。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪又大讚老公在旅行時全程湊B。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0f333f1d9562232c527d226ae8e9304/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_17.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪又大讚老公在旅行時全程湊B。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪參加活動時非常開心。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/44d108c45d23a845ba14c3b32c9eb83a/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪參加活動時非常開心。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪細心欣賞小朋友的演出。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/28cb299b127f516e9d6fdf389671c288/2025-01/KakaoTalk_20250110_125455839_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪細心欣賞小朋友的演出。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪提議新婚的蔣家旻先享受二人世界再生育。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7fb61b3c8ea59e7ad8be4f44abc98e25/2025-01/1_1_7.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪提議新婚的蔣家旻先享受二人世界再生育。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱千雪爆老公好享受做爸爸。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0df599826ec367dbd3899afd8f596677/2025-01/2_1_6.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱千雪爆老公好享受做爸爸。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>談到囝囝避免接觸電子產品，問到會玩什麼？她笑說：「玩我囉！第時唔畀佢打機，咪就要跟父母玩，每日我放工就會同佢玩具、讀書，但佢應該開心，我哋就好攰。」朱千雪又指囝囝容易照顧，畢竟要陪伴囝囝玩，所以要花心機同時間陪伴。談到可會追生B，她笑說：「搞掂呢個先，因為真係好攰！希望我哋熟習啲先再生多個。」\n\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n大讚老公全程揹BB\n\n</p>\n<p>對於可會鼓勵好友湯洛雯及新婚的蔣家旻生B，朱千雪坦言有提議她們可以享受人生先，因為有小孩後會想趕快回家，雖然放工休息，但要照顧小孩，所以也會懷念二人世界。提到早前一家可三口到首爾旅行時，老公全程揹BB獲網民大讚。她說：「佢係非常落手落腳湊BB，我負責餵奶，佢就會幫手沖涼，又會好樂意揹BB，亦好享受做爸爸，讚佢都好可以更加落力。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
